divs: Sighting DetailsI took some photos of odd looking cloud formation back in December 08. In these photos I seen many UFOS in the frames. I've been watching the sky a lot close now and still take photos all the time. I took a series of photos in Jan. 09 and again I spotted UFOS in the pics. I could not see or hear the UFOs and really didn't even know that anything was up there. To me this look like a disc shape craft.
